Package org.apache.tamaya.spisupport

Class DefaultMetaDataProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tamaya.spisupport.DefaultMetaDataProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetadataProvider
    public class DefaultMetaDataProvider
extends Object
implements MetadataProvider
    Default metadata provider implementation, which searches for all kind of entries formatted as [(META)key].metaKey=metaValue. All matching key/values are added to the meta data mapProperties for the given key as metaKey=metaValue meta entries.

        public Map<String,​String> getMetaData​(String property)
        Description copied from interface: MetadataProvider
        Access the current metadata for the given configuration context and key. The MetaData will be accessible from ConfigurationContext.getMetaData(String). Note that the metadata must not to be cached by it's consumers, so caching/optimazitation is delegated to this implementation.
        Specified by:
